snippet.title: KESSEN [PS2 Trailer]
snippet.description:
Kessen was first in the series of turn based strategy games released for ps2 system. Video is from one of demo I got when registered my ps2 in 2001. 

I little restored it in VirtualDub so quality is better than it was on demo disc.
